T1  - Obesity does not alter endometrial gene expression in women with endometriosis.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.rbmo.2020.03.015
A1  - Holdsworth-Carson, Sarah J
A1  - Chung, Jessica
A1  - Sloggett, Clare
