T1  - Using human genetics to understand the disease impacts of testosterone in men and women.
T3  - Comment in: Nat Rev Endocrinol. 2020 Apr;16(4):195 PMID: 32080496 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/32080496]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1038/s41591-020-0751-5
A1  - Ruth, Katherine S
A1  - Day, Felix R
A1  - Tyrrell, Jessica
A1  - Thompson, Deborah J
A1  - Wood, Andrew R
A1  - Mahajan, Anubha
A1  - Beaumont, Robin N
A1  - Wittemans, Laura
