T1  - Do endometrial lesions require removal? A retrospective study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12905-019-0756-8
A1  - Jiang, Ting
A1  - Yuan, Qing
A1  - Zhou, Qin
A1  - Zhu, Yiping
