T1  - Mechanisms of Adiponectin Action in Fertility: An Overview from Gametogenesis to Gestation in Humans and Animal Models in Normal and Pathological Conditions.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3390/ijms20071526
A1  - Barbe, Alix
A1  - Bongrani, Alice
A1  - Mellouk, Namya
